                </h3>
                <p className="text-xs text-gray-400">連接粉絲專頁以啟用「自動發文」與「品牌語氣分析」功能。</p>

                {/* SaaS OAuth Section */}
                <div className="bg-blue-900/10 p-4 rounded-lg border border-blue-900/30 mb-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 items-center">
                    <button 
